Package io.github.bananapuncher714.crafters.events

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CraftDisplayDestroyEvent
    Called whenever a CraftDisplay is going to be removed, or whenever its CraftDisplay.stop() method is called; Created on 2017-12-11
    CraftDisplayUpdateEvent
    Called whenever a CraftDisplay has to update its ItemDisplay; Created on 2017-12-07
    ItemDisplayCreateEvent
    Called whenever a CraftDisplay is about to create a new ItemDisplay; This is where you can use a custom ItemDisplay instead; Created on 2017-12-10
    ItemDisplayDestroyEvent
    Called whenever an ItemDisplay is going to be removed; Created on 2017-12-09
